Guilty Gear X2


he Midnight Carnival, is the third full installment in the Guilty Gear series 
of fighting games. First released in 2002, it has since received three updated 
versions. GGXX furthered the plot of the series and introduced new characters 
and gameplay mechanics. The graphics also appeared to be notably improved. It 
was much more commercially successful than its predecessor, Guilty Gear X.




	How to Install:


	STEP 1:		Extract file with 7z to anywhere you like.
			(note: Deafult installation location 
                        is 'OS':GamesGuilty_Gear_X2
			You can change the default installation directory if
                        you wish)


	STEP 2:		Double click 'setup.exe' in 'Freeman' folder.


	STEP 3:		Follow on screen instructions!
			*DO NOT INTERRUPT PROCESS ONCE EXTRACTION HAS BEGUN*
